high_descs: Turn around and go to the right and then right again to stand in front of the counter to the left of the stove.
Open the lower cabinet and pick up the pan from inside it.
Go right and stand in front of the microwave.
Put the pan in the microwave and turn it on and then take the pan out and shut the door.
Move left to face the lower cabinets to the left of the stove.
Open the lower cabinet on the left and put the pan inside and then shut the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed pan in a cabinet.

high_descs: Move to the cabinet to the left of the stove.
Open the bottom cabinet to the left of the stove and pick up the plate and close the door.
Move to the middle of the stove at the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the plate inside and heat it, retrieve the plate from the microwave and close the door.
Move to the cabinet to the left of you.
Place the plate on the bottom left cabinet and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Heat and replace the plate in the cabinet to the left of the stove.

high_descs: Turn right, then turn right again to cross the kitchen, then turn right again to reach the stove.
Open the cabinet to the left of the stove and grab the plate.
Turn right to face the microwave above the stove.
Warm the plate in the microwave, then take it out again.
Face the cabinet to the left of the stove and open it again.
Place the plate back in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed plate in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to your right, walk straight then turn right head to the cabinet on the left side of the stove
Open the cabinet then get the plate and close the cabinet
Turn to your right then face the microwave on your left
Open the microwave put in and out the plate then close the microwave
Turn around to your right, then head to the cabinet beside the stove
Open the cabinet then put in the plate and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place the warm plate inside the cabinet

high_descs: Go straight towards the kitchen table, then turn right, proceed straight until you reach the refrigerator, then turn right again and face the oven.
open the cabinet door next to the oven and beneath the counter top and remove a plate
face the stove top to the left of the toaster and start raising the plate to the microwave above the stove top
open the microwave and place the plate inside for several seconds, then remove it
lower the plate and turn to face the lower cabinet door to the left of the oven.
open the cabinet door and place the plate on the top shelf
anns.task_desc: Retrieve a plate from a cabinet and heat it up so you can return it to its original location

high_descs: Turn right go forward, then turn right, go forward then turn right to reach the stove.
Take the plate from the cabinet to the left of the stove.
Go to the stove to your right.
Warm the plate in the microwave, above the stove.
Turn around, then turn right, then turn back around to face the cabinet, the left of the stove.
Put the plate in the cabinet.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm plate in the cabinet.
